{"tid":2262113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國國會兩黨議員推出決議案要求認定新疆人權侵犯為種族滅絕","createTime":"2020-10-28T23:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T07:21:12.000Z","uid":204533,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f8bfd4adf70f865501bc2df5828c3aca603b9c5c","tid":2262113,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共和黨聯邦參議員科寧（Sen. John Cornyn，R-TX）和參議院外交關係委員會首席民主黨議員梅嫩德斯（Sen. Bob Menendez, D-NJ）率領多位共和、民主兩黨議員星期一（ 10月26日）推出新決議案，要求將中國在新疆維吾爾自治區侵犯維吾爾和其他少數民族人權的行為定性為種族滅絕。<br />\n<br />\n這些決議案將根據1948年《聯合國防止及懲治滅絕種族罪公約》追究北京當局的責任，並展開國際社會合作的協調工作，制止人權侵犯和虐待的行為。<br />\n<br />\n加入這項決議案聯署的還包括參議院外委會主席裡施參議員（Sen. Jim Risch, R-ID）、參議院情報委員會代理主席魯比奧參議員（Sen. Marco Rubio, R-FL） 、參議院外委會成員卡丁參議員（Sen. Ben Cardin, D-MD），默克里參議員（Sen. Jeff Merkley, D-OR）。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<strong><span class=\"red\">太長的時間以來，中國政府對數百萬維吾爾人和其他穆斯林進行了卑劣的種族滅絕運動，</span></strong>&rdquo;提出決議案的科寧參議員在聲明中說，&ldquo;這項決議認定這些罪行的本質，也是向中國這些駭人聽聞行為追究責任所邁出的第一步。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n梅嫩德斯參議員也在聲明中表示，&ldquo;毫無疑問，中華人民共和國對新疆維吾爾人進行了種族滅絕。制止種族滅絕的行為符合我們的國家安全以及價值觀，我們從挺身而出和為其發聲做起。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我希望特朗普總統和蓬佩奧國務卿能加入我們的行列，以他們的身份名義將這件事稱為種族滅絕，並與我們在國際社會的伙伴一起對此做出回應，&rdquo;梅嫩德斯在聲明中接著說。<br />\n<br />\n如果這項決議案獲得通過，參議院以&ldquo;種族滅絕&rdquo;一詞為新疆人權侵犯問題定調，結果很有可能將導緻美中緊張關係進一步升級，美國政府或能在法律層面上對中國政府採取新的措施。<br />\n<br />\n根據聯合國定義，<strong><span class=\"red\">種族滅絕行為包括殺戮、防止生育等行為，&ldquo;意圖摧毀一個國族、民族、種族或宗教團體的全部或部分。&rdquo;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n聯合國稱，根據國際法，種族滅絕為一種犯罪行為。<br />\n<br />\n........<br />\n<br />\n同時為美國國會暨行政當局中國委員會共同主席的魯比奧在聯署決議案後發表聲明表示，&ldquo;隨著愈來愈多證據表明中國政府和共產黨對新疆維吾爾人和其他少數民族犯下了令人髮指的罪行，我們必須弄清楚這些暴行的真正本質。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;自由國家必須趕緊團結起來，敦促（中國）結束這些罪行，並追究責任和訴諸正義，&rdquo;魯比奧在聲明中說。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-bipartisan-senators-resolution-uyghur-human-rights-abuses-genocide-20201027/5638446.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fus-bipartisan-senators-resolution-uyghur-human-rights-abuses-genocide-20201027%2F5638446.html&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=55070066\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-bipartisan-senators-resolution-uyghur-human-rights-abuses-genocide-20201027/5638446.html</a>"},{"pid":"a775f1afe3dc6ac5c7e084955ba6031357eea67e","tid":2262113,"uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:41:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1320817456043204609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1320817456043204609&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=ff11cc98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1320817456043204609&h=c9ea2f8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1320817456043204609</a>"},{"pid":"0b22ec6ebc2d757e0dd30c31e4e81920bccf3518","tid":2262113,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e981c9704a10a17cb7ae3e8ea6679e68c49e5bf6","tid":2262113,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ee4e4e0ce236d72ffa1ebefb15c53d46520e9d","tid":2262113,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:56:15.000Z","msg":"兩黨共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3ba495a49466ed835b8b791e783552cd1f161e","tid":2262113,"uid":135083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6d0f661ce887dd8d1a64ce7f73f24c04c8e1e41","tid":2262113,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5816c5a086d762c45dabd6fc0778f7bf1d0e6c21","tid":2262113,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:15:50.000Z","msg":"認定又點唔認定又點<br />\n又唔係救到佢地"},{"pid":"b2848979e0f62cb87edbddc4e5473a6d17d1a7eb","tid":2262113,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:17:36.000Z","msg":"民主黨一日有老細拜登+臭閪奶共黑婆存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬥黃唔會去到共和黨咁勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24fbfdd2bda19ca2132973ac462cb160ffe7c31","tid":2262113,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:19:49.000Z","msg":"成10年先還新疆公道，香港排隊要排到2029？"},{"pid":"dc0d063235a23db6e56ac5449b25ef66dc28560a","tid":2262113,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"隻小學生真係以為自己惡晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e635ca982ce2179f238492d9758cfacb6d7144c","tid":2262113,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0110fc8733f7d98ed40007700929e50db5561a","tid":2262113,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"連袁爸爸都開始推動香港係獨立民族<br />\n<br />\n可能有機會推埋香港係種族滅絕"},{"pid":"f7bdf21ed931c2430f8d368b5141f81507cf4388","tid":2262113,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"Rubio<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}